snippet.title: Lai Bari Lai Bari ( लै बरी लै बरी ) - Trishna Gurung || Official Video
snippet.description:
Trishna Gurung on Spotify: https://spoti.fi/3fx2Tqc

The wait is finally over !!
My new song ‘लै बरी लै बरी’ is out now on YouTube. 
This track is a piece of my heart, wrapped in music, and I can’t wait to share it with you. Your love and support mean the world—let’s make this journey unforgettable together. Much Love Trishna Gurung  

Singer / Lyrics / Compose: TRISHNA GURUNG
Music Producer / Mix Mastered : BIZU KARMACHARYA
Direction : PAVEL UDAS

Actors : EVA GIRI / KUNSANG BOMJAN
Supporting Actors : NIKITA GOPALI / ROSNI RAYAMAJHI / DIPSHA KC

Dance Choreographer : LOSINA SHAKYA
MUA : AASHNA CHACHAN

Camera / Drone : MANISH ADHIKARY
Asst Camera : BIKASH KHADGI 
Edit : BIZU KARMACHARYA
Colorist : MAHESWOR SHRESTHA
Production Manager : RAJU SHRESTHA

Special Thanks
DAD & MOM, SONAMLA LAMA, CHANG SHRESTHA, NISCHAL SADASHANKAR, BUDDHA RATNA MANANDHAR (GURJUDHARA HOMESTAY), AMIR JOSHI, AMRIT SHRESTHA, NISHA HAMAL (TANDAV DANCE ACADEMY), PRATIBHA CHETTRI, MANDHAVI CHETTRI AND THE COLLAB

Follow me on:
Spotify: https://spoti.fi/3fx2Tqc​
Fan page:    / trishnagurun​.  ​.
Instagram:    / trishnaguru​.  ​.
Facebook:    / trishna.guru​.  ​.

From 22nd to 24th September, the Top 16 teams of Nepal are set to clash across three days of high-intensity action - with 5 matches daily starting at 17:30 GMT +5:45.

They’re battling for their share of the $5,000 prize pool.

snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer - Hindi | Rishab Shetty | Rukmini | Vijay Kiragandur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films — the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar — and the visionary, National Award–winning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend – Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend – Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations.

Lyrics :- 
Sath Pheron Se Bandha
Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan ………

snippet.description:
Nepali Song Lyrical Video "Kodo Fulyo Barima" By Udit Narayan Jha & Deepa Jha only on Music Nepal official YouTube channel.

Unauthorized downloading and duplicating on YouTube channel may lead to claim/strike by YouTube.

The right for this video is provided by Music Nepal Pvt.Ltd.

Nepali Song - Kodo Fulyo Barima
Movie - Muglan
➤ Singer – Udit Narayan Jha & Deepa Jha
➤ Lyrics – Loknath Sapkota
➤ Music – Suresh Adhikari
➤ Editor – Rabin Deshar

Lyrics :- 

चरी र रि ररि रै 
वर्ष र दिनको  
रमाइलो चाड 
गाँउघरमा आइपुग्यो
नेपालीजनको महान् पर्व आँगनमा आइपुग्यो
हो....दसैँ आयो

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा
लरी लै 
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

साइको घडी हातैमा
लरीलै ढाका टोपी ढल्क्यो शिरैमा
तिमीलाई नै सुहाउँछ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो
ला...ला..ला

पिढीँमा बसी औँला भाँची छोराको आउने दिन गन्दैथिन्
दसैँको दिन ति बूढीआमै आइपुग्दा छोरो दङ्गै छिन्

भादौरे झरी सुकेर जाँदा असोजमा नौलो रङ्ग छाउँछ
ठूलाको हाता सानाको माथा आशिष दिँदै दसैँ आउँछ

हे एक्लै भयो चमेली लरी लै
राख मलाई पिङ्गको सिटैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
हो फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
मुगलानै जाने आफन्तलाई 
घर आऊ भनी डाक्दछन्
हो.. ती पल्ला घरे लाहुरेदाइले
परदेशको कोसेली बाँड्दैछन्
लाहुरेनी भाउजू मुसुमुसु हाँस्दै
भित्र र बाहिर गर्दैछन्

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा लरी लै
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
नेपालीलाई सुहाँउछ बरी लै 
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो
 
दसैँ आयो

hi.title: जॉली एलएलबी 3 | ट्रेलर | अक्षय कुमार | अरशद वारसी | सुभाष कपूर | सिनेमाघरों में 19 सितंबर
hi.description:
अभी टिकट बुक करें - https://bookmy.show/JollyLLB3 | https://link.district.in/DSTRKT/phJollyLLB3

जब दो जॉली होंगे, तो होगा डबल - कॉमेडी, बवाल और क्लेश!
#JollyLLB3 का ट्रेलर अभी रिलीज़ हुआ है। #JollyLLB3 सिनेमाघरों में 19 सितंबर को।

स्टार स्टूडियो18 प्रस्तुत करता है
जॉली एलएलबी 3
लिखित और निर्देशित: सुभाष कपूर
निर्माता: आलोक जैन, अजीत अंधारे
सह-निर्माता: नरेन कुमार, डिंपल खरबंदा 
लाइन निर्माता: कांगड़ा टॉकीज़
कलाकार: अक्षय कुमार, अरशद वारसी, सौरभ शुक्ला
कार्यकारी निर्माता: शशि ठाकुर, रोहित जयसवाल 
पर्यवेक्षक निर्माता: शिवाजी दासगुप्ता 
फोटोग्राफी के निदेशक: रंगराजन रामबद्रन
संपादक: चन्द्रशेखर प्रजापति 
सिंक ध्वनि और ध्वनि डिजाइन: दारा सिंह
संगीत निर्देशक: अमन पंत, अनुराग सैकिया, विक्रम मॉन्ट्रोज़ 
गीतकार: राम कुमार सिंह, पुनीत शर्मा, मेघा बाली, अखिल तिवारी, परधान
एक्शन डायरेक्टर: परवेज़ शेख 
पृष्ठभूमि संगीत: मंगेश धाकड़े
संगीत लेबल: पैनोरमा संगीत
अतिरिक्त पृष्ठभूमि स्कोर: श्रीनाथ म्हात्रे
पोशाक बनाने वाला: वीरा कपूर ई.ई 
प्रोडक्शन डिजाइनर: मानसी ध्रुव मेहता

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Release Date: 18 July 2025

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: HAQ | Official Teaser | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Shazia Bano takes her husband Abbas to court after he abandons her and their children, sparking a national battle over faith, women’s rights, and justice. Inspired by the landmark Supreme Court judgement of Mohd. Ahmed Khan vs. Shah Bano Begum. Haq is the story of one woman’s fight for her rights and justice. 

Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

HAQ is a fictionalized and dramatized version of events stated in the book titled ‘Bano: Bharat ki Beti’ written by Jigna Vora.

Cast- Yami Gautam, Emraan Hashmi, Vartika Singh, Danish Husain, Sheeba Chadha,
Aseem Hattangady
Directed by- Suparn S Varma
Written by- Reshu Nath
Produced by- Vineet Jain
Produced by- Vishal Gurnani, Juhi Parekh Mehta, Harman Baweja
Co- Producer- Amrita Pandey
Co-Producer- Suparn S Varma, Rowena Baweja, Sandeep Singh
Supervising Producer- Vicky Jain

Director of Photography- Pratham Mehta
Associate Producer- Kalpesh Damani

Executive Producers- Ramesh G Yadav, Priyanka Mehrotra

snippet.title: PERFECT - Guru Randhawa, Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari
snippet.description:
Sir to pairan de takk,
You so perfect! 💯

Adding to the fire of ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’, Guru Randhawa joins the party with PERFECT! 🔥 Composed and written by Guru Randhawa, Rony Ajnali and Gill Machhrai, the song is sung by Guru Randhawa. Starring our Sunny ‘Varun Dhawan’ and Tulsi ‘Janhvi Kapoor’ in the video, get ready to watch, vibe, and replay on loop! 🚀

#PERFECT #GuruRandhawa #VarunDhawan #janhvikapoor

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer Review
snippet.description:
Kantara Chapter 1 trailer sets up a massive, visually rich epic with jaw-dropping aesthetics and scale, hiding most of its action for the big screen. Though a bit overloaded, Rishabh Shetty’s passion shines through — this film feels like a true cinematic gamble worth the wait. #Kantara #PJExplained #thePJ

Swagat cha Day 3 ma 2025 PUBG MOBILE Nepal Series (PMNS) Grand Finals ko! Sabai kura Top 16 team haruma aayera cha — aja ko antim 5 ota match-haru 17:45 GMT +5:45 bata suru hune cha.

$5,000 prize pool line ma cha, ra sirf sabai bhanda shaktishali team ley crown jitne cha. Nepal ko Champion ko Crown kasle lagcha?

Finalist Teams (Top 16):
BROS ESPORTS
TRIBE AEROMACY
T2K ESPORTS
HIDDEN LEAF ESPORTS
THE GAMING BROSKIS
4 DEATH MACHINE
SKD ESPORTS
DRS GAMING
BAGH ESPORTS
NOTYOUR FIRENATION
DREAM TO DESTINATION
NEPX ESPORTS
THE WESTMINSTER COLLEGE
GORE ESPORTS
4YONKO ROYAL JUTTI
HORAA ESPORTS

Day 3 ko Map Schedule: 
Match 1: Sanhok 
Match 2: Erangel 
Match 3: Miramar 
Match 4: Sanhok 
Match 5: Erangel

📺 Antim din ajha ho— pratyek move mahatwapurna cha, pratyek shot ko aartha cha!

snippet.title: नवरात्रि स्पेशल :ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी | Durga Mata Aarti | Om Jai Ambe Gauri | Durga Ma Ki Aarti
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि स्पेशल : ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी | Durga Mata Aarti | Om Jai Ambe Gauri | Durga Ma Ki Aarti

Description:
Welcome to this divine rendition of ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी — the powerful Durga Mata Aarti that invokes the blessings of Maa Durga during the auspicious occasion of Navratri. This Durga Ma Ki Aarti is filled with devotion and praise, making it an ideal way to worship Goddess Durga and seek her blessings for strength, prosperity, and peace.

🌸 ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी is a traditional prayer sung with love and reverence to honor Goddess Durga, who is revered as the embodiment of Shakti (power). The Aarti resonates with a divine energy, especially during the Navratri festival, when devotees come together to celebrate the nine days of the goddess.

🔔 This Navratri special video will fill your heart with positivity, divine energy, and spiritual peace. Whether you are participating in the Navratri celebrations or seeking to connect with the divine energy of Maa Durga, this Aarti will bring you closer to the goddess.

✨ Submerge yourself in the divine melody of Maa Durga's Aarti and experience her powerful presence in your life.

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe, like, and share this video with your friends and family to spread the divine blessings of Durga Ma.

🕉️ Om Jai Ambe Gauri – Jai Maa Durga! 🕉️

en.description:
नवरात्रि स्पेशल : ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी | Durga Mata Aarti | Om Jai Ambe Gauri | Durga Ma Ki Aarti

Description:
Welcome to this divine rendition of ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी — the powerful Durga Mata Aarti that invokes the blessings of Maa Durga during the auspicious occasion of Navratri. This Durga Ma Ki Aarti is filled with devotion and praise, making it an ideal way to worship Goddess Durga and seek her blessings for strength, prosperity, and peace.

🌸 ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी is a traditional prayer sung with love and reverence to honor Goddess Durga, who is revered as the embodiment of Shakti (power). The Aarti resonates with a divine energy, especially during the Navratri festival, when devotees come together to celebrate the nine days of the goddess.

🔔 This Navratri special video will fill your heart with positivity, divine energy, and spiritual peace. Whether you are participating in the Navratri celebrations or seeking to connect with the divine energy of Maa Durga, this Aarti will bring you closer to the goddess.

✨ Submerge yourself in the divine melody of Maa Durga's Aarti and experience her powerful presence in your life.

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe, like, and share this video with your friends and family to spread the divine blessings of Durga Ma.

Lyrics:-
Timi Tirai Chha Mero Dhyana
Timrai Naam Ma Pass Gare Yo Jyana
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Timlai Mero Yaad Aaune Bhaye 
Gartheu Hola Bhet Huni Upaye
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Dherai Pachhi Mukh Dekhna Payeko
Tesaile Ho Ma Najik Aayeko
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Bhetda Matrai Mukh Thikka Garauchhau
Yek Din Bhetchhau Barshaudin Harauchhau
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Timlai Bhetda Yekohoro Heri Rahu
Lagchha Malai Angalo Beri Rahu
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Ris Garnelai Dekhaudai Hasera
Bachna Man Chha Dui Mutu Gasera
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Timi Juna Timi Nai Hau Tara
Timi Nai Hau Jibanko Sahara
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Chokho Maya Kinera Paidaina
Timi Bhaye Malai Koi Chaidaina
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Bar Binako Pipalu Hunalai
Parni Chhaina Jibanbhar Runalai
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Maya Garchhu Man Dekhi Hera
Timlai Matrai Baschhu Ma Samjhera
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Raatma Batti Chahe Jhai Gharaima
Ma Bachyachhu Mayako Bharaima
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Timlai Paye Ma Bhagyamani Ho
Natra Jiban Royerai Jani Ho
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

snippet.title: Wakka Lagdo Sansar - bekcha - Jodi No.1 Title Song [Lyrical Video]
snippet.description:
#wakkalagdosansar #Jodino1 #bekcha 
Wakka Lagdo Sansar is the original soundtrack for an amazing web series Jodi No. 1 made with love, soul and perseverance by brilliant human beings with big dreams. When you have the time and mind, go catch it here:

The first episode: https://youtu.be/lCakw0IyOt4
Full Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@UC3uDjw2Sg4EgPfZeAR_Q2rQ 

I would like to pay respects to the brave fighters, martyrs of the current movement in Nepal. The whole nation mourns this massive loss and is forever indebted to all of  you.  I am sending out prayers to the bereaved family and friends.

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

Audio Credits:
(Produced, Mixed and Mastered by) https://www.instagram.com/begendra_official
https://www.instagram.com/anmolz_music
Guitars: https://www.instagram.com/bishalchhetriguitar/
Sansic Productions

i'm in instagram sometimes - https://www.instagram.com/b3kcha
and mail me here, if you feel it should get to me: songsbybekcha@gmail.com

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

आदि सृष्टि में विधि को, श्रुति उपदेश दिया
शिल्प शस्त्र का जग में, ज्ञान विकास किया
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ऋषि अंगिरा ने तप से, शांति नही पाई
ध्यान किया जब प्रभु का, सकल सिद्धि आई
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

रोग ग्रस्त राजा ने, जब आश्रय लीना
संकट मोचन बनकर, दूर दुख कीना
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

जब रथकार दम्पती, तुमरी टेर करी
सुनकर दीन प्रार्थना, विपत्ति हरी सगरी
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

एकानन चतुरानन, पंचानन राजे
द्विभुज, चतुर्भुज, दशभुज, सकल रूप साजे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ध्यान धरे जब पद का, सकल सिद्धि आवे
मन दुविधा मिट जावे, अटल शांति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

श्री विश्वकर्मा जी की आरती, जो कोई नर गावे
कहत गजानन स्वामी, सुख सम्पत्ति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा प्रभु जय श्री विश्वकर्मा
सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma Prabhu Jai Shri Vishwakarma
Sakal Srishti Ke Karta Rakshak Shruti Dharma
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Aadi Srishti Mein Vidhi Ko, Shruti Updesh Diya
Shilp Shastra Ka Jag Mein, Gyaan Vikas Kiya
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rishi Angira Ne Tap Se, Shaanti Nahi Paayi
Dhyaan Kiya Jab Prabhu Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aayi
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rog Grast Raja Ne, Jab Aashray Leena
Sankat Mochan Bankar, Door Dukh Keena
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Jab Rathkaar Dampati, Tumri Ter Kari
Sunkar Deen Prarthana, Vipatti Hari Sagari
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Ekanan Chaturanand, Panchanan Raaje
DviBhuja, ChaturBhuja, Dashabhuja, Sakal Roop Saaje
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Dhyaan Dhare Jab Pad Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aave
Man Duvitha Mit Jaave, Atal Shaanti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Shri Vishwakarma Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Nar Gaave
Kahat Gajanan Swami, Sukh Sampatti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma Prabhu Jai Shri Vishwakarma
Sakal Srishti Ke Karta Rakshak Shruti Dharma
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

snippet.title: नवरात्रि का दूसरा दिन - जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ - Maa Brahmacharini Aarti - Navratri 2nd day
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि का दूसरा दिन - जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ - Maa Brahmacharini Aarti - Navratri 2nd day

तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

श्याम बाबा के रोज नए नए भजन सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़ें रहे व् नए नए भजनों का आनंद उठाये भजन पसंद आये तो कमेंट में '' जय श्री श्याम " जरुर लिखें || Jai Shree Shyam 🌹🌹

⭐Song : Brahmcharini Mata  Aarti
⭐Singer : Upasana Mehta
⭐Lyrics : Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)

▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️Lyrics✍️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️▪️ 
जय अंबे ब्रह्माचारिणी माता।
जय चतुरानन प्रिय सुख दाता।
ब्रह्मा जी के मन भाती हो।
ज्ञान सभी को सिखलाती हो।
ब्रह्मा मंत्र है जाप तुम्हारा।
जिसको जपे सकल संसारा।
जय गायत्री वेद की माता।
जो मन निस दिन तुम्हें ध्याता।
कमी कोई रहने न पाए।
कोई भी दुख सहने न पाए। 
उसकी विरति रहे ठिकाने।
जो ​तेरी महिमा को जाने।
रुद्राक्ष की माला ले कर।
जपे जो मंत्र श्रद्धा दे कर।
आलस छोड़ करे गुणगाना।
मां तुम उसको सुख पहुंचाना।
ब्रह्माचारिणी तेरो नाम।
पूर्ण करो सब मेरे काम।
भक्त तेरे चरणों का पुजारी।
रखना लाज मेरी महतारी।

जिसको जपे सकल संसारा।

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

#Roblox #foltyn

snippet.title: Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa
snippet.description:
#durgamaa  #durgachalisa #दुर्गाचालीसा 
Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa
Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa

नमो नमो दुर्गे सुख करनी।
नमो नमो दुर्गे दुःख हरनी॥

निरंकार है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
तिहूं लोक फैली उजियारी॥
शशि ललाट मुख महाविशाला।
नेत्र लाल भृकुटि विकराला॥

रूप मातु को अधिक सुहावे।
दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥

ऋद्धि-सिद्धि दै करहु निहाला।

तुम्हरो यश मैं सदा सुनाऊं ॥

दुर्गा चालीसा जो कोई गावै।
सब सुख भोग परमपद पावै॥

देवीदास शरण निज जानी।
करहु कृपा जगदम्ब भवानी॥

Experience the divine power of Maa Durga with this soul-stirring rendition of Mahishasura Mardini Stotram, beautifully sung by Keya Acharya. 🌺✨

This Mahalaya 2025 Special Bhakti Song invokes the strength, courage, and blessings of Devi Durga, celebrating her victory over Mahishasura. The stotram is chanted during Durga Puja, Navratri, and especially on Mahalaya, marking the arrival of Devi on Earth. 🙏

🎶 Song Credits:
SINGER: Keya Acharya
CHANNEL: Bhakti Yug Mantraa

🔥 Listen to this devotional song daily to feel divine energy, inner peace, and Maa Durga’s protection. Perfect for Durga Puja, Mahalaya mornings, and Navratri bhajans.

snippet.title: शारदीय नवरात्रि स्पेशल - Maa Brahmacharini Ki Aarti - जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माता- माँ ब्रह्मचारिणी की आरती
snippet.description:
Bhakti Bhajan Sagar Presents ...

Song : Brahmacharini Maa Aarti
Singer :  Ruchi Khandelwal
Producer : Bhakti Bhajan Sagar
Music : Shankar Maheshwari
Lyrics : Traditional
Channel : Bhakti Bhajan Sagar
Copyright : Bhakti Bhajan Sagar

जय अम्बे ब्रह्मचारिणी माता।जय चतुरानन प्रिय सुख दाता॥

ब्रह्मा जी के मन भाती हो।ज्ञान सभी को सिखलाती हो॥

ब्रह्म मन्त्र है जाप तुम्हारा।जिसको जपे सरल संसारा॥

जय गायत्री वेद की माता।जो जन जिस दिन तुम्हें ध्याता॥

कमी कोई रहने ना पाए।कोई भी दुख सहने न पाए॥

उसकी विरति रहे ठिकाने।जो तेरी महिमा को जाने॥

रद्रक्षा की माला ले कर।जपे जो मन्त्र श्रद्धा दे कर॥

आलस छोड़ करे गुणगाना।माँ तुम उसको सुख पहुँचाना॥

ब्रह्मचारिणी तेरो नाम।पूर्ण करो सब मेरे काम॥

भक्त तेरे चरणों का पुजारी।रखना लाज मेरी महतारी॥
